"marker MOD6 mod-inline"></span> <!--[PREMOD7]--><span class=3D"marker PREM=
OD7 mod-inline"></span><p class=3D"topic-paragraph">A guard is hired to pro=
tect two safes in separate locations: <em>S</em>1 contains $10,000 and <em>=
S</em>2 contains $100,000. The guard can protect only one safe at a time fr=
om a safecracker. The safecracker and the guard must decide in advance, wit=
